room_title: Escape room "The Kidnapping" by Breakout Games - Knoxville in Knoxville
review: Our group chose to do the Kidnapping scenario and we had a blast! This was so much fun and our game master Ryan was awesome. We will definitely be back.

room_title: Escape room "The Kidnapping" by Breakout Games - Knoxville in Knoxville
review: Kidnapping was well thought out. The lighting, puzzles and theme were right on. The staff helped make the experience awesome. Only wish we lived closer to do other rooms.

room_title: Escape room "The Kidnapping" by Breakout Games - Knoxville in Knoxville
review: We went as a party of eight and we loved it! We did the Kidnapping room. Very difficult but we made it out in time! All I can say is GO! Well done!

room_title: Escape room "The Kidnapping" by Breakout Games - Knoxville in Knoxville
review: This place is awesome! A great team building exercise, or if you're like my group, a chance to see who is the smartest! Alex was great, and it was an experience we will never forget! Will definitely be returning!
